			I think Spyder is on target.<br><br>Create some content. Maybe incorporate some of the pvp elements of SWG/Planetside into the pvp servers. Rewards, a point system, etc.<br><br>What I don't seem them doing is balancing all the classes. That's a huge pandora's box that's best left closed. And the training issue (not really a problem on TZ), I don't know how that can really be solved.  That's simply a behavior problem that can even occur on blue servers. It's appears that SZ draws that type of player. /shrug.<br><br>Something I'd like to see is giving pvp-ed players a "non-combatant" status, prohibiting them from engaging in any pvp for 1 hour. This gives you time to safely get your corpse while preventing CCing and bind rushing.<br><br>It is a shame they locked that thread.<br><br>Yaroop
